{"tid":2231824,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"合約員工想加人工","createTime":"2020-10-06T03:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T00:27:32.000Z","uid":327401,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ceeb9528c7e9e4f56a68979e2bef18a99aea88e8","tid":2231824,"uid":327401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:01:38.000Z","msg":"背景：<br />\n今年六月比人炒左，之後有個同事帶咗我去一間ibank 做Ops，人工cut左$2000，八月返工。3個月試用期。一年合約員工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做左2個月左右，好Chur，成日OT。上手1730即走，我最早都1900，一般1930-2130收工，唔係我慢，係workload 明顯多咗。<br />\n<br />\n合約員工得一個月B仔，Permanent 大約有8-10個月。所以自己好唔願意又OT，paid又cut左，又冇人地咁多B仔。（但冇表現又唔會轉Permanent ）<br />\n<br />\n自問對得住份糧，唔敢講underpaid。<br />\n<br />\n由於都幾辛苦，想係試用期前，提出加人工，但個市又好差，但其實我都想捱一年轉Permanent。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來講，我目的係加人工，之後又轉Permanent。大家點睇？"},{"pid":"6a3ca4761c15e0692e82ceb47dff00e9db260b69","tid":2231824,"uid":126731,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:04:01.000Z","msg":"銀行真係唔使諗.&nbsp;同老闆講提早轉Permanent都有D可能.&nbsp;今年叫加人工同叫佢炒你無分別.&nbsp;仲要銀行OPS位咁易找人replace你."},{"pid":"00029ee8d34b1b2355b7256f35b3f41fa1f3541c","tid":2231824,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"如果真係覺得自己unpaid,&nbsp;轉工係唯一方法証明自己個market&nbsp;value.&nbsp;"},{"pid":"d8f5face0473f3629aa305becbb2e2dfbed4498d","tid":2231824,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:04:14.000Z","msg":"睇你搏唔搏 <br />\n你預搏輸左就工都冇"},{"pid":"b183041c5846f4fddad30e2749aca1b7adc0f2ce","tid":2231824,"uid":7248,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"老實都係做左兩個月姐 如果真係想轉perm 就忍多排啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身in個陣係講明唔chur?"},{"pid":"f693bb83be51027c8156dd200b9b6a62f9a2347f","tid":2231824,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:09:46.000Z","msg":"點解咁撚正咁多b 仔"},{"pid":"a5c7d37af5302333face